      "id": "PopularPost275593",
      "post_content": "Many people consider land destruction to be \"unfun,\" but it's an integral component to Magic in all formats, from Standard all the way to Vintage.   \n  \nYour mana base is just another resource that you have to protect if you want to win...just as [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt) zaps your life total and [Hymn to Tourach](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach) mutilates your hand, land destruction screws up your mana base--and like any other strategy, it has its counter-strategies...if your friend is killing you with massive discard, you'd sideboard in [Leyline of Sanctity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity). If your friend is killing you with [Armageddon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armageddon), you sideboard in [Sacred Ground](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sacred Ground). What's the big deal?",
      "posted_by": "Werewolf-",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost275593\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Many people consider land destruction to be \"unfun,\" but it's an integral component to Magic in all formats, from Standard all the way to Vintage. <br/><br/>Your mana base is just another resource that you have to protect if you want to win...just as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a> zaps your life total and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hymn to Tourach\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hymn to Tourach\">Hymn to Tourach</a> mutilates your hand, land destruction screws up your mana base--and like any other strategy, it has its counter-strategies...if your friend is killing you with massive discard, you'd sideboard in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leyline of Sanctity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity\">Leyline of Sanctity</a>. If your friend is killing you with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Armageddon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Armageddon\">Armageddon</a>, you sideboard in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sacred Ground\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sacred Ground\">Sacred Ground</a>. What's the big deal?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '275593'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div cla